one of the best shows out today could even possibly top smallville because the pilot was better than smallvilles and is the best show on TV today better than person of interest, supernatural, touch and fringe through what I've seen i cant wait till the next episode the episode is about plot: After a violent shipwreck, billionaire playboy Oliver Queen was missing and presumed dead for five years before being discovered alive on a remote island in the Pacific. When he returns home to Starling City, his devoted mother Moira, much-beloved sister Thea, and best friend Tommy welcome him home, but they sense Oliver has been changed by his ordeal on the island. While Oliver hides the truth about the man he's become, he desperately wants to make amends for the actions he took as the boy he was.

